'''席夢娜‧西蒙斯'''(Simone Simons)，全名席夢娜‧喬安娜‧瑪莉亞‧西蒙斯，是一位荷蘭籍的女高音。她是荷蘭[[交響金屬|交響金屬]]樂團[[黯黑史詩|黯黑史詩]]的主唱。

==早年生活==
西蒙斯從小就對音樂十分感興趣。她12歲時開始<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.simonesimons.nl/bio.php |title=Simone Simons - Official Website |publisher=Simonesimons.nl |date= |accessdate=2012-11-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130112072407/http://www.simonesimons.nl/bio.php |archivedate=2013-01-12 }}</ref>，學了2年的長笛。14歲時，她開始接受流行歌唱訓練，但一年後，因為受到了交響金屬樂團[[日暮頌歌|日暮頌歌]]的影響<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/SimoneSimons/status/268536462738329600 |title=Twitter / SimoneSimons: Fav NW album is 'Oceanborn' |publisher=Twitter.com |date= |accessdate=2012-11-18 |archive-date=2016-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405162450/https://twitter.com/simonesimons/status/268536462738329600 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，她轉而改受傳統的聲樂訓練。在合唱團中唱了數個月後，她加入了[[黯黑史詩|黯黑史詩]]。<ref name="anewagedawns1">{{cite web |url=http://www.anewagedawns.com.br/site/?page_id=53 |title=Simone Simons : A NEW AGE DAWNS – Fã Clube Oficial Brasileiro do Epica |publisher=Anewagedawns.com.br |date= |accessdate=2012-11-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927195153/http://www.anewagedawns.com.br/site/?page_id=53 |archivedate=2013-09-27 }}</ref> 

==黯黑史詩==
2002年末，西蒙斯取代了海蓮娜‧邁可森，成為[[黯黑史詩|黯黑史詩]]的新主唱。截至目前為止，他們共發行了4張專輯，巡演足跡遍佈全球。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.simonesimons.nl/bio.php |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-07-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130112072407/http://www.simonesimons.nl/bio.php |archivedate=2013-01-12 }}</ref>

==私人生活==
在加入[[黯黑史詩|黯黑史詩]]時，西蒙斯與[[馬可·傑生|馬可·傑生]]是情侶關係。兩人交往4年後分手。<ref>[http://live-metal.net/interviews_epica_simone_simons.html|publisher=http://live-metal.net/]</ref><br />
2013年10月2日，西蒙斯誕下了與[[幸運之星|幸運之星]]的鍵盤手[[奧利佛‧帕羅泰|奧利佛‧帕羅泰]]所生的兒子，文森‧帕羅泰。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.smoonstyle.com/ |title=SmoonStyle A Beauty & Lifestyle Blog by Simone Simons |publisher=Smoonstyle.com |date=2014-07-28 |access-date=2014-08-16 |archive-date=2018-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714062606/https://www.smoonstyle.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{cite web |url=http://epica.nl/news/553-the-epica-family-expands/ |title=The Epica family expands |publisher="http://epica.nl'' |date=April 24, 2013 |accessdate=April 24, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130427102001/http://epica.nl/news/553-the-epica-family-expands |archivedate=2013年4月27日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://epica.nl/news/565-simone-and-oliver-have-a-little-boy/|title=Simone and Oliver have a little boy!|publisher=http://epica.nl|date=October 4, 2013|accessdate=October 4, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004220829/http://epica.nl/news/565-simone-and-oliver-have-a-little-boy/|archivedate=2013年10月4日}}</ref>同年12月，西蒙斯在部落格中宣佈了自己與奧利佛‧帕羅泰的婚事。<ref>{{cite web |last=Simons |first=Simone |url=http://www.smoonstyle.com/2013/12/vrolijk-kerstfeest.html |title=Vrolijk Kerstfeest! ❯SmoonStyle |publisher=Smoonstyle.com |date=2013-12-25 |accessdate=2014-07-28 |archive-date=2021-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326062845/https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Maven+Pro%3Aregular%7CLora%3Aitalic%2Cregular&subset |dead-url=no }}</ref><br />
西蒙斯有一個名為「Smoonstyle」的部落格，內容主要圍繞在美妝、美食以及生活經歷分享。

